  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a comal over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the diced pork shoulder and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Stir in the sumac, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the shredded phyllo and cook, stirring constantly, until golden brown, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the lemon juice and chopped parsley.",
    "Form the mixture into a knafeh shape and cook for an additional 2 minutes, until crispy and golden brown.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
  ],
